<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rüya Günlüğü - Hoşgeldiniz</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html,
        body {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #f8f8f8;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            overflow-y: auto;
            height: 100%;




            background-image: url('/images/bck.png');
            /* Görselin yolu */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }




        .landing-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 10px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 900px;
            background-color: rgba(45, 3, 59, 0.6);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 78, 205, 1);




        }

        .landing-container h3 {
            color: #ff4ecd;
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .landing-container p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .landing-container button {
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background-color: #ff4ecd;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .landing-container button:hover {
            background-color: #ff74d4;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #2d033b;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(255, 78, 205, 0.4);
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .navbar .logo {
            color: #ff4ecd;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .navbar ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .navbar ul li a {
            color: #f8f8f8;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar ul li a:hover {
            color: #ff4ecd;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #f8f8f8;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #ff4ecd;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>


    <%- include('partials/_navbar') %>



        <div class="landing-container">
            <p>Rüyalarınızı günlüğünüze kaydedin, bilinçaltınızın derinliklerini keşfedin,
                rüyalarınızı analiz ederek anlamlandırın ve onları büyüleyici hikayelere dönüştürerek hayal gücünüzü
                yeniden inşa edin!</p>


            <% if (!user) { %>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/login'">Hadi Başlayalım</button>
                <% } %>
        </div>

</body>

</html>